{"tid":1968291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】台灣捐 700 萬口罩送歐洲國家 歐洲議會議員：支持台灣入世衛","createTime":"2020-04-11T14:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T14:39:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcda05cd5aedfbcfdbf17a105741ba963360f0b","tid":1968291,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"立場新聞 Stand News立場新聞 Stand News<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】台灣捐 700 萬口罩送歐洲國家 歐洲議會議員：支持台灣入世衛<br />\n<br />\n立場報道2020/4/11 &mdash; 19:29<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200411-11_GjKIu_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200411-11_GjKIu_1200x0.png&h=8432cefa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎在全球蔓延，各地防疫物資短缺，台灣今月宣布首波國際人道援助行動，捐贈 1000 萬個口罩給美國及歐洲，當中 700 萬個已送抵歐洲，陸續運送到法國、荷蘭、瑞士等國家。台灣外交部昨（10 日）在 FB 上傳三名歐洲政要感謝台灣捐贈的影片，包括歐洲議會友台小組主席凱勒（Michael Gahler），他在片段中表示，在這段抗疫期，合作團結非常重要，「這也是我為甚麼非常支持將台灣納入世界衞生組織」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣外交部昨天（10 日）在 FB 表示，第一波國際人道援助 700 萬個口罩已送抵歐洲，分別送往荷蘭、義大利、西班牙、法國、德國、波蘭、捷克、比利時、盧森堡、英國、瑞士和教廷，給第一線急需口罩的醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發布的片段中，有三名歐洲政拍片感謝台灣，包括歐洲議會友台小組主席凱勒（Michael Gahler）、法國國民議會友台小組副主席伯多赫（Eric Bothorel）和瑞士首都伯恩（Bern）市長葛拉費瑞（Alec von Graffenried）。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n外交部又宣布將展開第二波國際人道援助行動，將再捐贈 600 萬個醫療口罩，支援疫情嚴重的國家，包括北歐及中東歐地區的歐盟會員國、美國疫情嚴重的州、拉丁美洲暨加勒比海地區國家、新南向政策目標國家及其他友好國家等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n守護言論與新聞自由<br />\n立場新聞，寸步不退<br />\n<br />\n每月贊助$200，支持立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%8D%90-700-%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%80%81%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%258D%2590-700-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%2580%2581%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=433177a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%258D%2590-700-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%2580%2581%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%2F&h=0dc22219\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%8D%90-700-%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%80%81%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B/</a>"},{"pid":"b1929502d5f8b99eab7dbfcbaaa68a90626a9d02","tid":1968291,"uid":146285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好"},{"pid":"8e74b72f7ccba37f21998bfbe1adefaadb1abc46","tid":1968291,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"口罩外交<br />\n屈機到, 睇黎會列入歷史書"},{"pid":"6203d889433af2e0f3a32e9e054663d1a67cf1ca","tid":1968291,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04